        "explanation": "10 groups of 6 is easy: just put a 0 after 6."
      },
      {
        "subgoalLabel": "Subtract one group",
        "instruction": "Take away one group of 6.",
        "work": "60 − 6 = 54.",
        "explanation": "9 groups is one less than 10 groups, so subtract 6."
      },
      {
        "subgoalLabel": "State the answer",
        "instruction": "What is 9 × 6?",
